</div>
<div class="fn" id="FN3">
<p id="P6"><strong>Author Contributions:</strong> Conception and design: J.A. Dodson, T.E. Murphy, M.G. Nanna, T.M. Gill, S.I. Chaudhry.</p>
<p id="P7">Analysis and interpretation of the data: J.A. Dodson, A. Hajduk, H.M. Krumholz, T.E. Murphy, S. Tsang, M.G. Nanna, S.I. Chaudhry.</p>
<p id="P8">Drafting of the article: J.A. Dodson, A. Hajduk, T.E. Murphy, M.G. Nanna, S.I. Chaudhry.</p>
<p id="P9">Critical revision of the article for important intellectual content: J.A. Dodson, A. Hajduk, M. Geda, H.M. Krumholz, T.E. Murphy, M.E. Tinetti, M.G. Nanna, T.M. Gill, S.I. Chaudhry.</p>
<p id="P10">Final approval of the article: J.A. Dodson, A. Hajduk, M. Geda, H.M. Krumholz, T.E. Murphy, S. Tsang, M.E. Tinetti, M.G. Nanna, R. McNamara, T.M. Gill, S.I. Chaudhry.</p>
